ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[The investigation of the preceding 3 local cases of Japanese encephalitis
identified in the Hong Kong SAR this year did not reveal evidence of onward
transmission of the virus. The increased number of local cases this year,
however, requires continued vigilance. - Mod.CP]
